=Phoenix's Homecoming=

00:00:56.094 --> 00:00:58.948
=Episode 23=

00:01:02.759 --> 00:01:03.399
Your Highness.

00:01:03.840 --> 00:01:05.159
Imperial Guard informants report.

00:01:06.040 --> 00:01:07.799
The ambassador sent
by King Liang of Qi State

00:01:08.359 --> 00:01:09.560
is not the Seventeenth Prince.

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:12.719
I fear the delegation has been replaced.

00:01:13.719 --> 00:01:14.359
Furthermore,

00:01:15.200 --> 00:01:16.560
look at the delegation outside.

00:01:16.719 --> 00:01:18.079
They're all powerfully built.

00:01:19.079 --> 00:01:21.280
They don't look like
scholarly diplomats.

00:01:21.560 --> 00:01:22.519
They look more like

00:01:23.480 --> 00:01:24.840
highly skilled warriors.

00:01:34.480 --> 00:01:36.319
Regarding the fire at Weiyang Palace,

00:01:36.799 --> 00:01:38.359
since you escaped,

00:01:38.719 --> 00:01:40.920
it was only proper
to inform His Majesty and me.

00:01:41.640 --> 00:01:43.079
Now you suddenly reappear.

00:01:45.879 --> 00:01:47.599
The timing
is quite convenient, isn't it?

00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:00.640
Your Highness, are you implying

00:02:01.719 --> 00:02:03.480
that you doubt my identity?

00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:05.799
Why wouldn't I doubt it?

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:07.640
After that great fire,

00:02:07.640 --> 00:02:09.479
you vanished without a trace,

00:02:09.639 --> 00:02:12.879
allowing rumors to slander
the royal family as traitors.

00:02:13.639 --> 00:02:14.919
Now you suddenly appear,

00:02:15.599 --> 00:02:17.400
seeking to regain control of the state.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:20.719
Are you planning
to betray the nation again?

00:02:23.879 --> 00:02:26.319
Your Highness, your words
are full of insinuations.

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:28.439
Could it be you suspect

00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:32.199
that I am secretly colluding
with the Grand Princess,

00:02:34.080 --> 00:02:35.199
and that we intend to draw

00:02:37.159 --> 00:02:38.280
swords against Chen State?

00:02:57.680 --> 00:02:58.560
I

00:02:59.919 --> 00:03:02.280
never share a drink
with those about to die.

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:11.120
I never waste words on fools.

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:16.080
Before today,

00:03:16.479 --> 00:03:17.560
the throne was Chen's.

00:03:18.159 --> 00:03:19.120
After today,

00:03:19.400 --> 00:03:20.599
it may not be.

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:24.719
The Grand Princess committed treason.
The evidence is clear.

00:03:24.759 --> 00:03:25.599
Spare no one!

00:03:25.960 --> 00:03:26.800
Kill them all!

00:03:27.319 --> 00:03:29.560
- Attack!
- Attack!

00:03:52.039 --> 00:03:53.360
Lady Xie, why are you here?

00:03:53.920 --> 00:03:54.840
With all this going on,

00:03:54.840 --> 00:03:55.560
I had to come.

00:03:56.199 --> 00:03:56.879
In a crisis,

00:03:57.000 --> 00:03:59.039
we should stand together.

00:04:06.879 --> 00:04:08.560
Your Highness, we're outnumbered.

00:04:08.599 --> 00:04:10.159
Let's find a safe place.

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:11.280
- Let's go.
- Go.

00:04:16.279 --> 00:04:17.120
Come, Your Highness.

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:19.079
Don't let them escape!

00:04:21.240 --> 00:04:22.160
Jinxiu!

00:04:22.439 --> 00:04:23.680
Your Highness, go!

00:04:24.319 --> 00:04:25.879
Jinxiu!

00:04:26.399 --> 00:04:27.920
Your Highness, go!

00:04:29.920 --> 00:04:31.800
- No, no!
- Go now!

00:04:32.079 --> 00:04:33.160
Jinxiu!

00:04:34.839 --> 00:04:36.199
Jinxiu!

00:05:24.040 --> 00:05:25.120
You're not afraid of fire?

00:05:26.120 --> 00:05:27.319
You aren't afraid of fire?

00:05:27.600 --> 00:05:28.279
Fire?

00:05:30.040 --> 00:05:31.079
I was afraid once.

00:05:32.920 --> 00:05:33.839
But fires of the abyss

00:05:33.959 --> 00:05:35.399
couldn't burn me to death.

00:05:36.920 --> 00:05:38.759
What can earthly fire do to me now?

00:05:40.480 --> 00:05:41.240
I don't believe it.

00:05:41.959 --> 00:05:43.079
I don't believe it!

00:05:50.959 --> 00:05:51.800
Sheng Yunlin.

00:05:54.040 --> 00:05:55.839
Do you know I despise

00:05:57.079 --> 00:05:59.480
your fearless, reckless attitude most?

00:06:00.920 --> 00:06:02.000
We are both women,

00:06:02.519 --> 00:06:04.160
so why must I always be constrained?

00:06:04.800 --> 00:06:07.079
Every path I took led to a dead end.

00:06:10.079 --> 00:06:10.839
And you?

00:06:11.399 --> 00:06:12.439
Since you were born,

00:06:14.040 --> 00:06:16.120
you were an unconstrained princess.

00:06:16.399 --> 00:06:17.639
Why?

00:06:22.680 --> 00:06:23.639
Do you know

00:06:24.120 --> 00:06:25.839
how long I've been trapped
in this place?

00:06:28.480 --> 00:06:30.639
The water in Yeyou Court was so cold.

00:06:31.639 --> 00:06:32.639
Even later,

00:06:33.079 --> 00:06:34.759
when I became Regent Princess,

00:06:35.160 --> 00:06:37.759
I would still wake in terror
from nightmares

00:06:38.319 --> 00:06:39.759
about that water.

00:06:40.839 --> 00:06:42.519
Everything you see now

00:06:42.839 --> 00:06:44.399
is what I achieved

00:06:44.639 --> 00:06:46.360
by walking step by step on knife edges.

00:06:46.879 --> 00:06:47.720
And you?

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:49.839
When I was buried in flames,

00:06:49.839 --> 00:06:50.920
where were you?

00:06:58.879 --> 00:07:01.040
Your precious brother,
whom you protected diligently,

00:07:01.519 --> 00:07:03.360
do you know

00:07:04.480 --> 00:07:05.959
he gave it his tacit approval?

00:07:06.920 --> 00:07:08.399
He wanted you to fake your death.

00:07:08.759 --> 00:07:11.199
He wanted to change your identity
and marry you.

00:07:11.600 --> 00:07:13.879
If not for his tacit approval back then,

00:07:13.920 --> 00:07:15.639
it wouldn't have proceeded so smoothly.

00:07:18.759 --> 00:07:19.920
Now you know.

00:07:21.040 --> 00:07:21.959
Regret it now?

00:07:22.199 --> 00:07:23.000
I have no regrets.

00:07:24.480 --> 00:07:25.720
Huo Wan, I have no regrets.

00:07:27.240 --> 00:07:27.959
To survive,

00:07:27.959 --> 00:07:29.360
Chen Yu must be the new emperor.

00:07:30.399 --> 00:07:31.399
Even if it weren't him,

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:34.800
the Chen State could never
be handed over to your Huo family.

00:07:36.079 --> 00:07:36.759
Huo Wan,

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:38.639
do you know why I chose you

00:07:38.879 --> 00:07:41.319
as consort
for the new emperor back then?

00:07:44.279 --> 00:07:46.120
Not just because you're
Chancellor Huo's girl,

00:07:49.439 --> 00:07:50.199
but because

00:07:51.040 --> 00:07:52.279
you're wise and composed.

00:07:52.959 --> 00:07:53.879
I thought harmony

00:07:54.199 --> 00:07:55.560
between Emperor and Empress

00:07:56.279 --> 00:07:57.680
would make a fine story.

00:08:00.120 --> 00:08:01.079
If not,

00:08:04.639 --> 00:08:06.600
you should still carve your own path.

00:08:11.240 --> 00:08:12.120
But I was wrong.

00:08:14.800 --> 00:08:15.720
I was wrong.

00:08:18.920 --> 00:08:21.160
You ended up trapped
in this gilded cage.

00:08:37.600 --> 00:08:39.120
This Chen State harem

00:08:39.559 --> 00:08:41.720
is a man-eating den of demons!

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:44.000
Do you think only the Empress is insane?

00:08:44.200 --> 00:08:45.799
His Majesty is worse.

00:08:46.279 --> 00:08:47.799
He knows you're the Grand Princess.

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:52.759
He'll never let Xie Fei
live in this world.

00:08:53.240 --> 00:08:54.120
One is family.

00:08:55.159 --> 00:08:56.039
The other is beloved.

00:08:56.639 --> 00:08:58.240
Sheng Yunlin, tell me.

00:08:58.600 --> 00:09:01.840
Tell me how to choose
without losing either!

00:09:01.879 --> 00:09:02.759
Huo Wan,

00:09:03.320 --> 00:09:05.120
this is your excuse for treason?

00:09:10.039 --> 00:09:11.399
You go easy on yourself.

00:09:12.600 --> 00:09:14.399
You think I lost to you?

00:09:15.799 --> 00:09:16.360
No.

00:09:18.240 --> 00:09:19.480
I lost to fate.

00:09:20.080 --> 00:09:20.960
Lost to fortune.

00:09:21.559 --> 00:09:24.000
And lost to the shackles of womanhood.

00:09:24.879 --> 00:09:26.000
Everyone wants me dead.

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:27.279
Fine!

00:09:27.720 --> 00:09:28.639
Come at me!

00:09:29.120 --> 00:09:31.639
All of you shall join me in death!

00:10:16.320 --> 00:10:19.600
You can't kill me.

00:10:20.159 --> 00:10:21.360
I will possess

00:10:22.519 --> 00:10:25.960
supreme power.

00:11:36.200 --> 00:11:36.960
Huaiyong.

00:11:41.759 --> 00:11:42.639
This time,

00:11:46.399 --> 00:11:47.519
I'm here.

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:01.200
The Empress plotted rebellion
with King Liang,

00:12:01.600 --> 00:12:03.360
killed by the Imperial Guard
and Sheng army.

00:12:04.879 --> 00:12:05.799
Wei Ling will clear

00:12:06.480 --> 00:12:08.279
all remaining traitors
by tomorrow night.

00:12:09.360 --> 00:12:09.840
Yes.

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:13.559
Grand Tutor Xie conspired
with the Empress,

00:12:14.200 --> 00:12:16.200
attempting to assassinate me
and seize power.

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:18.799
His treasonous ambition is plain to see.

00:12:19.600 --> 00:12:20.919
The Empress was right.

00:12:21.320 --> 00:12:22.480
I can't tolerate Xie Fei.

00:12:23.559 --> 00:12:24.759
No one under heaven shall have

00:12:25.480 --> 00:12:27.080
what I can't possess.

00:13:31.079 --> 00:13:31.679
Your Highness.

00:13:32.720 --> 00:13:33.240
What?

00:13:35.480 --> 00:13:36.960
His Majesty doesn't even allow me

00:13:38.600 --> 00:13:39.720
to mourn my dead husband?

00:13:40.159 --> 00:13:40.720
Your Highness,

00:13:41.840 --> 00:13:44.840
Lady Yunfei was Xie Fei's betrothed.

00:13:44.960 --> 00:13:45.559
Not you.

00:13:46.679 --> 00:13:48.519
You hold the Grand Princess title.

00:13:48.840 --> 00:13:50.879
Escorting a traitor's coffin
violates propriety.

00:13:51.559 --> 00:13:53.679
Please return to the palace with me.

00:13:55.240 --> 00:13:56.679
Your Highness, please think twice.

00:13:57.600 --> 00:13:58.799
If you advance further,

00:13:59.720 --> 00:14:01.240
how can the Xie family be spared?

00:14:04.639 --> 00:14:05.399
His Majesty said

00:14:06.759 --> 00:14:07.840
the Xie family rebelled

00:14:09.720 --> 00:14:10.720
and Xie Fei was executed.

00:14:11.200 --> 00:14:13.360
The Xies are merely exiled
to the border,

00:14:13.960 --> 00:14:15.039
not exterminated.

00:14:16.279 --> 00:14:18.399
If you remain defiant,

00:14:18.960 --> 00:14:19.840
the Xie family

00:14:20.480 --> 00:14:22.200
shall be wiped out completely.

00:14:29.679 --> 00:14:31.039
Your Highness, please return.

00:14:34.240 --> 00:14:35.320
My entire clan

00:14:35.840 --> 00:14:38.080
kowtows in gratitude
for His Majesty's mercy.

00:14:53.799 --> 00:14:54.519
Good girl,

00:15:01.399 --> 00:15:02.960
having you in my son's life

00:15:04.759 --> 00:15:05.600
is enough.

00:15:08.480 --> 00:15:09.279
Take care.

00:15:12.720 --> 00:15:13.360
Go!

00:15:28.639 --> 00:15:29.399
Your Highness.

